      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like im constantly performing. like every single day is just this exhausting charade of trying to act \"normal\" so people dont look at me weird. i feel like i'm from a different planet or something. i'm just so tired of trying to belong when it's so obvious i never will.",
